    summary: 'Update the contract end date',
    description:
      "Update or add an end date to a contract. Ending a contract early will impact draft usage statements, truncate any terms, and remove upcoming scheduled invoices. Moving the date into the future will only extend the contract length. Terms and scheduled invoices are not extended. In-advance subscriptions will not be extended. Use this if a contract's end date has changed or if a perpetual contract ends.\n",
    stainlessPath: '(resource) v1.contracts > (method) update_end_date',
